headline: Exclusive-First Indian space startups picked for Indo-US defence programme, sources say
summary: Seven Indian private companies have been chosen for a first-of-its-kind India-U.S. space and defence collaboration programme, unlocking a lucrative and strategic market for Indian firms, said three...
